00:02:34.876 --> 00:02:35.690 align:middle line:84%
>>BOBBY AKART:
Thank you, George.

00:02:35.690 --> 00:02:35.960 align:middle line:90%
>>NOORY: Welcome.

00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:36.460 align:middle line:90%
Good to talk to you again.

00:02:36.460 --> 00:02:37.720 align:middle line:84%
>>AKART: Well, thank you
very much for having me on.

00:02:37.720 --> 00:02:38.250 align:middle line:90%
I appreciate it.

00:02:38.250 --> 00:02:39.820 align:middle line:84%
